=======

Combining multimedia resources for an engaging experience of cultural heritage

\cite{ardito:combining}

The application of alternate reality techniques to cultural heritage promises particular benefits to young people, as cultural heritage sites often arouse little involvement in them, especially when the site's present day appearance bears few traces of its original stature.